channel.title: Tops on Graham Wheeler's Random Forest
channel.description: Recent content in Tops on Graham Wheeler's Random Forest

item.description: Graham Wheeler is a software engineering leader at Microsoft. He has worked as a software engineer and engineering leader and data science director at companies like Microsoft, Google, and eBay, as well as his own startup in the 1990’s producing one of the earliest Internet firewall and VPN products. Originally from South Africa, Graham has a Ph.D. in computer science and a bachelor’s degree in mathematics and computer science from the University of Cape Town.
